The '''motor pool''' was a [[Hangar/Legends|hangar]] in [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba Desilijic Tiure's]] [[Jabba's Palace/Legends|desert palace]] where his vehicles were stored. It included dozens of [[Bantha-II cargo skiff/Legends|cargo skiffs]], [[Landspeeder/Legends|landspeeders]], [[Speeder bike/Legends|speeder bikes]] and the large [[Sail barge/Legends|sail barge]] [[Khetanna/Legends|''Khetanna'']]. Jabba's chief [[Technician/Legends|mechanic]] [[Barada/Legends|Barada]] worked and slept there.<ref name="AFQitP" />

